<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ث غ ا:</span> <span class="c2">(الثُّغَاءُ)</span> صَوْتُ الشَّاةِ وَالْمَعْزِ وَمَا شَاكَلَهُمَا وَ <span class="c2">(الثَّاغِيَةُ)</span> الشَّاةُ وَالرَّاغِيَةُ الْبَعِيرُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>